l Polish:**\n    *   *Tone Check:* Encouraging, specific, literary.\n    *   *Connecting to the Cipher Subplot:* Briefly mention how the linear \"unlocking\" of the code mirrors the linear \"unlocking\" of his moral position.\n\n8.  **Output Generation:** (This matches the provided good response.)]",
